[SN]TITLE[SN]
100 Women: Senegal's powerful grandmother

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Grandmothers in Senegal are proving to be a powerful force in efforts to improve the lives of children, especially girls, in villages in Senegal.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
29 December 2016 Last updated at 01:20 GMT
Egge Kande is one of them, urging girls not to drop out of school or fall pregnant.
Producer: Dina Demrdash; camera: Maxime Le Hegarat
